which I think is fantastic.

00:33:10.800 --> 00:33:14.150
But the point that we're
all sort of getting at is

00:33:14.150 --> 00:33:17.800
that institutions have
been transformed.

00:33:17.800 --> 00:33:20.790
I mean Cathy touched on this
talking about the New Republic,

00:33:20.790 --> 00:33:23.930
which has been around
for a substantial portion

00:33:23.930 --> 00:33:25.230
of American history.

00:33:25.230 --> 00:33:27.200
It's been around since
the 19th century.

00:33:27.200 --> 00:33:29.310
The nation has been
around that long.

00:33:29.310 --> 00:33:32.450
Poetry's been around for over
a hundred years, and so on.

00:33:32.450 --> 00:33:37.590
