poetry and literature as it sort

00:33:37.590 --> 00:33:40.800
of lived in places such
as literary magazines

00:33:40.800 --> 00:33:43.760
or magazines was not
reflecting reality

00:33:43.760 --> 00:33:45.840
for a very long period of time.

00:33:45.840 --> 00:33:48.880
