to be reality, those magazines

00:33:58.320 --> 00:34:01.480
in our culture have
become transformed.

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:03.700
And so, I don't think
it will ever go back

00:34:03.700 --> 00:34:05.480
to something that it was before.

00:34:05.480 --> 00:34:07.520
